properties.headline: Tornado Watch issued January 11 at 5:18AM CST until January 11 at 12:00PM CST by NWS New Orleans LA
properties.description:
THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS ISSUED TORNADO WATCH 11 IN
EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS

IN LOUISIANA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 22 PARISHES

IN SOUTHEAST LOUISIANA

EAST FELICIANA        IBERVILLE             JEFFERSON

WEST FELICIANA

IN MISSISSIPPI THIS WATCH INCLUDES 6 COUNTIES

IN SOUTHERN MISSISSIPPI
